projects.title: Go-Go Yogurt
projects.description: Go-Go Yogurt brings the fun of yogurt with the kick of an enrgy drink! Sponsored by TLC and Momma June (from the hit show Here comes Honey Boo Boo). Go-Go Yogurt comes in four great flavors: Mountain Dew, Cheesy Dorito, Disco Powder, and Dr. Pepper.
